criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — defined the decision question, objectives, inputs, and assumptions;  
Represent — described model structure, metrics (EPS, leverage, ROIC vs WACC), and visualization plan;  
Implement — showed code, parameterization, ran script, and reported numeric outputs/tables and charts;  
Validate/Evolve — ran sensitivity checks on ROIC, interpreted robustness, and refined recommendation;  
Reflect — summarized trade-offs and delivered a final split allocation recommendation.
